cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI. 

This paper deals with Handwritten Text Processing systems, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper uses artificial neural networks, which is a common technique in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves text analysis, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves logic analysis, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and geometric analysis, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics). However, since the paper focuses more on the text analysis aspect, cs.CL and cs.AI are less likely than cs.LG and cs.GR.
